{"type": "article", "id": 26679, "title": "Pharrell 和三叶草合作第二波，以及，Acne 的春夏眼镜系列不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-05-11T10:54:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5264, "name": "童装"}, {"id": 27473, "name": "夏季系列"}, {"id": 2355, "name": "眼镜"}, {"id": 2443, "name": "杂志"}, {"id": 620, "name": "韩国"}, {"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 1886, "name": "冰淇淋"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 27474, "name": "Glossier"}, {"id": 1612, "name": "Mac"}, {"id": 4949, "name": "Guess"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 5170, "name": "Moncler"}, {"id": 5622, "name": "Fossil"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607133010WRxbIm5MnZdQfro8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Italy-s-Moncler-first-quarter-sales-rise-more-than-expected,691338.html#.VzKFcIQrJQZ\"><b>Moncler 一季度销售胜预期</b></a>｜意大利奢侈羽绒品牌 Moncler 周二宣布一季度销售额获得 18% 增长，超出预期， 有赖于中国及日本市场的良好表现以及在美国批发渠道的强劲。一季度销售额达到 2.373 亿欧元（约合 2.701 亿美元），超过汤森路透 2.22 亿的预期。由于全球 175 家直营旗舰店的有机增长，零售销售额上涨了 22% 至 1.7 亿欧元。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/H-M-to-open-first-store-in-Puerto-Rico-in-June,691245.html#.VzKGzYQrJQY\"><b>H&amp;M 波多黎各开了第一家店</b></a>｜瑞典快时尚品牌 H&amp;M 近日宣布波多黎各第一家店将于 6 月 9 日正式开幕，位于圣胡安购物商场（The Mall of San Juan），占地 31000 平方英尺（约合 2880 平方米）。将售卖男女装、童装，店内还有专售饰品、内衣和彩妆的店中店。4 月 H&amp;M 在印度的新德里开出第 4000 家门店。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Abercrombie-Fitch-expands-Middle-East-operations,690924.html#.VzKJEIQrJQY\"><b>Abercrombie &amp; Fitch  扩张中东业务</b></a>｜Abercrombie &amp; Fitch  宣布将与中东的零售伙伴 Majid Al Futtaim 集团合作，扩张其在中东的业务，Abercrombie &amp; Fitch 从 2013 年开始已经在阿联酋及科威特开出 8 家门店，特许代理协议包括旗下的 Abercrombie、Hollister 、Abercrombie &amp; Fitch 品牌在沙特阿拉伯、阿曼等地的扩张。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Fossil-stocks-tumble-on-weak-earnings-report,691377.html#.VzKPpYQrJQY\"><b>Fossil 收入疲软</b></a>｜Fossil  集团周二宣布截至 4 月 2 日的一季度财政结果，这一季度全部市场及全品类都面临挑战。恒定汇率下，全世界净销售额减少 7% 至 4890 万美元，欧洲区净销售额恒定汇率下降低了 8% 至 1810 万美元。而手表部门降低了 8%、珠宝部门降低了 11%，皮具部门降低了 2%。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/denim/guess-jeans-retail-store-moscow-10427766/\"><b>Guess 莫斯科开店</b></a>｜洛杉矶品牌 Guess 宣布很快将在莫斯科市中心的 Europeisky 商场开旗舰店。同时还表示将“在俄罗斯联邦的首都创立这样直接管理的 Showroom，为其许可及批发伙伴加强销售网络及提供有效支持”。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">还记得我们之前报道过“菲董”Pharrell 今夏要和 Adidas 再度合作，推出的“Pink Beach” 系列吗？目前<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/pharrell-adidas-pink-beach-delivery-2\">第二波的 lookbook 也已经发布</a>，预计 5 月 12 日上市：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132950ZPIcQBuUfNbCKSz1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132950oKvLVNFjwPG58BeX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132951GtTaj710e6PRHn9Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132952VZFRAC4y69oDwThu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132952MhaPT3sQyLvldIrC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071329536mAPCt1TgnIwhfpi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132953XH2yeJlgsbrDYtuz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132954zE7jOWuSQiUKvmNL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">此外，还一并推出了<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/pharrell-adidas-pink-beach-kids\">童装系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132955hLq9yREW3Xd5So1U.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132955KSQsj3M6LUBfA0Cl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132956AwHPSnGN6UkEhZua.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132956nJNQxqoSe5U7XzH4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713295772t3YPJf6h58bkjs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>已经为 Gucci、Lanvin、Saint Laurent、Alexander McQueen 等各大品牌拍摄广告、走秀的短发超模 Ruth Bell，最近<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/ruth-bell-miu-miu-vogue-korea/\">身穿 Miu Miu 为韩国版 Vogue 拍摄杂志封面及大片</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132957zrQc9Y6aG3u72ONE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132958rHxy5ul3Scm68Qoh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6275\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071329594XdK3kzrg7iPFARh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6275\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132959H96ANug0pO7mijwr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713300070teM9TKNUuyY2Si.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133000vJhKxzeMkWjt0cap.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">夏天到了，彩妆品牌也纷纷推出冰淇淋主题的系列彩妆。<a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/5/10/11650810/mac-soft-serve-glossier-ice-cream\">MAC 宣布冰淇淋系列将在 5 月 26 日官网上市</a>，6 月 2 日登陆门店，其中包含 12 色奶油眼影比如薄荷绿、淡蓝和金属色，眉笔也有粉色、薄荷绿、淡紫等颜色。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133001rNg7vBCnEsDR5I2u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.29375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071330015PWsTXJYarUFkn12.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">美妆初创公司 Glossier 和据称“纽约最美味冰淇淋”的<a href=\"http://www.morgensternsnyc.com\"> Morgenstern's Finest Ice Cream </a>合作，推出了樱桃、薄荷、玫瑰冰淇淋口味的唇膏：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713300237S6B5H4LDhuktri.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133002JtzbWwXSYP651cI9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">瑞典品牌 Acne Studios 发布了<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/05/09/acne-studios-new-ss16-sunglasses/#slide-15\"> 2016 年春夏的眼镜系列</a> ：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133003c39lACx76G8tsa20.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133003ZgL3SnP9qDIJ1EyY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071330049uhg734EwfMj6Fdv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071330042YwsSrfNgIW9Pb0O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071330048mYW3ZRgaP5ubGtC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133005n5bIGgahT7NMCXJV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133006aWwO3PQKYu4BjpeA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133006b5SR7MfgWCTkjemF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133006NmV3OEcxdfDlMXjW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Guess 最新的春夏系列牛仔广告：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133007kCXBe2Wy9R3Dm0AH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133007Mr9tBwVbo1OkL2Cs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67300832\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133008Mt2qC1Lbnw7j9cWZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.06125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133008MpaFi2krGnAXCHV8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71554994\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071330098KtmIzdSkORTYjQN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72534332\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133010K1it2ulxDOSJof0m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69915764\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n"}